.container
    .jumbotron.subhead
        %h1
            = @page_title = "Modules"
            %p.lead Game Settings
    %section
        .row
            = partial('modules_sidebar')
            .col-sm-9
                .page-header
                    %h1= @page_sub_title = "Classes"
                :markdown
                    Classes allow the player to pick a specific class at the beginning of the game which gives them special abilities. Classes can be used on any map type, however care must be taken to balance them properly. Players can then change their class ingame with the `/class` command.

                .table-responsive
                    %table.table.table-striped.table-condensed
                        %thead
                            %tr
                                %th{:style => "min-width: 300px;"} Classes Element
                                %th Description
                                %th
                        %tbody
                            %tr
                                %td
                                    %span.highlight
                                        %code= html_escape('<classes> </classes>')
                                %td A node containing a single class or a group of classes.
                                %td
                            %tr
                                %th{:colspan => "2"} Sub-elements
                                %th Value/Children
                            %tr
                                %td
                                    %span.highlight
                                        %code= html_escape('<class> </class>')
                                %td
                                    A single player class.
                                %td
                                    %span.label.label-default Class Sub-elements

                %h5 Class Attributes
                .table-responsive
                    %table.table.table-striped.table-condensed
                        %thead
                            %tr
                                %th Attribute
                                %th Description
                                %th Value
                                %th Default
                        %tbody
                            %tr
                                %td
                                    %code name
                                %td
                                    %span.label.label-danger Required
                                    The classes name, must be a unique.
                                %td
                                    %span.label.label-primary String
                                %td
                            %tr
                                %td
                                    %code description
                                %td
                                    Description shown in the
                                    %code /classes
                                    command.
                                %td
                                    %span.label.label-primary String
                                %td
                            %tr
                                %td
                                    %code longdescription
                                %td
                                    Description shown in class picker menu.
                                %td
                                    %span.label.label-primary String
                                %td
                            %tr
                                %td
                                    %code icon
                                %td
                                    Icon shown in the class picker menu.
                                %td
                                    %a{:href => "/reference/inventory#material_matchers"} Single Material Pattern
                                %td
                            %tr
                                %td
                                    %code family
                                %td
                                    %span.label.label-danger Required
                                    "group" of classes (ghost squadron is "ghost").
                                %td
                                    %a{:href => "/modules/classes"}  Class Family Name
                                %td
                            %tr
                                %td
                                    %code sticky
                                %td
                                    If set to
                                    %code true
                                    players can't change the class mid game, instead they have to rejoin.
                                %td
                                    %span.label.label-primary true/false
                                %td false
                            %tr
                                %td
                                    %code default
                                %td
                                    Specify if the class is the default class for new players.
                                    %br
                                    %i One class must be set as the default.
                                %td
                                    %span.label.label-primary true/false
                                %td false
                            %tr
                                %td
                                    %code restrict
                                %td
                                    If set to
                                    %code true
                                    only OP's can use this class.
                                %td
                                    %span.label.label-primary true/false
                                %td false

                %h5 Class Sub-elements
                .table-responsive
                    %table.table.table-striped.table-condensed
                        %thead
                            %tr
                                %th Element
                                %th Description
                                %th Type
                        %tbody
                            %tr
                                %td
                                    %span.highlight
                                        %code= html_escape('<kit>')
                                %td
                                    The kit given to players using this class.
                                %td
                                    %a{:href => "/modules/kits"} Kits

                :markdown
                    Example

                        <classes family="ghost" sticky="true">
                            <class name="Demon" default="true" description="Smoke and Fire!" icon="fireball">
                                <kit>
                                    <potion duration="oo" amplifier="2" ambient="true">damage resistance</potion>
                                    <potion duration="oo" amplifier="1" ambient="true">speed</potion>
                                    <item slot="8" amount="16" material="cooked beef"/>
                                    <item slot="1" amount="5" name="`3Grenade" grenade="true" material="ender pearl"/>
                                </kit>
                            </class>
                        </classes>
